<Base title="Privacy Policy — SnapJar" description="How SnapJar handles your data: tools run locally, nothing is uploaded; cookies and advertising explained.">
  <header class="head"><div class="wrap"><p class="kicker">Legal</p><h1>Privacy Policy</h1></div></header>
  <div class="content">
    <p><em>Last updated: June 2026</em></p>
    <h2>The short version</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Our tools run <b>entirely in your browser</b>. The numbers you type and the images you select are processed on your device and are <b>never uploaded</b> to us.</li>
      <li>We don't require an account and don't ask for personal details to use a tool.</li>
      <li>We use cookies and third-party advertising to keep the site free.</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Information we collect</h2>
    <p>We don't collect the contents you enter into our tools. Like most websites, our hosting and analytics may record standard technical data such as IP address, browser type, device and pages visited, used for security and to understand aggregate usage.</p>
    <h2>Cookies and advertising</h2>
    <p>We use cookies and similar technologies, including for advertising. Third-party ad partners (such as Google) may use cookies or device identifiers to show and measure ads under their own privacy policies. Where required, we will ask for your consent before non-essential cookies are set, and you can manage or withdraw consent at any time. You can also opt out of personalized ads via your ad provider's settings and control cookies in your browser.</p>
    <h2>Image and file tools</h2>
    <p>Images, PDFs and other files you open in our tools are read and processed <b>locally in your browser</b>. They are not transmitted to any server and are discarded when you close or leave the page.</p>
    <h2>Third-party services</h2>
    <p>To run a fast, free site we rely on a few third parties that may receive standard request data such as your IP address: our host (Netlify), content-delivery networks that serve open-source tool libraries (jsDelivr, unpkg), and, where you choose to use them, optional Google Drive / Dropbox import. When advertising is enabled, Google AdSense is also used. Each operates under its own privacy policy.</p>
    <h2>Your rights (GDPR &amp; India's DPDP Act)</h2>
    <p>Because our tools don't collect or store your personal data, there is typically nothing for us to retrieve or erase about you. Where any personal data is processed (for example, advertising identifiers after you consent), you have the right to access, correct, delete or restrict it, to withdraw consent at any time, and to lodge a complaint with your data protection authority. To exercise any right, contact us at the email below and we'll respond promptly.</p>
    <h2>Children's privacy</h2>
    <p>The site is not directed to children under 13 and we do not knowingly collect their personal information.</p>
    <h2>Changes</h2>
    <p>We may update this policy; the date above reflects the latest revision.</p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions or data requests? Email <b>sankettoraskar.business@gmail.com</b>.</p>
  </div>
</Base>
